|RKBThe Uruk are a loose tribe of marauding orcs which live in the Darkwind
area, looting and pillaging small settlements. The Uruk value strength
and stamina over useless thought or a pretty face. They are a warlike race
that trains for battle from birth to death, acquiring a degree of proficiency
in the use of all weapons. They are particularly adapted to living in
marginal areas like shallow caves, or fetid swamps.

